extends base.pug

block scripts
  script(src='/static/index.js')

block style 
    style
      include ../static/style.css

block content 
    section#introSection 
        div Welcome To Shashwat Dance Academy
        div.small Eat Sleep Dance Repeat
    section#sponsorsSection 
        h3 Our Sponsors
        div#sponsors
            img(src="/static/img/sponsor1.jpg" class="spImage" alt="sponsor image")
            img(src="/static/img/sponsor2.jpg" class="spImage" alt="sponsor image")
            img(src="/static/img/sponsor3.jpg" class="spImage" alt="sponsor image")
            img(src="/static/img/sponsor4.jpg" class="spImage" alt="sponsor image") 
    section#missionSection 
        h3 Our Mission
        div.card
            h4 Dance perfection
                div.card-box
                  div.card-img
                     img(src="/static/img/mission1.jpg")
                  div.card-content
                     p Perfection in each and every step is most important part of dance.      
        div.card
            h4 Dance the way you like 
                div.card-box
                  div.card-img
                     img(src="/static/img/mission2.jpg")
                  div.card-content
                     p Most important thing is interest in dancing, dancing your own way is not wrong.
        div.card
           h4 Expert teaching
                div.card-box
                  div.card-img
                     img(src="/static/img/mission3.jpg")
                  div.card-content
                     p From our side, we want to give the best guidance to anyone who is dedicated towards dancing. 
        div.card
            h4 Competitive Success             
                div.card-box
                  div.card-img
                     img(src="/static/img/mission4.jpg")
                  div.card-content
                     p There is only one way to prove yourself to be the best, by defeating others.   